 and Resident Historian of the Roosevelt Institute and author of The Last 100 Days: FDR at War and at Peace, to discuss FDR's personal triumphs, his hidden struggles and his international legacy. Could or should he have predicted the divided Europe that followed hot on the heels of a hard-fought peace?\n\nWith thanks to the archivists at the Franklin D Roosevelt Presidential Library. \n\nPresented by Matthew Parris.\n\nProduced by Sarah Goodman for BBC Audio Bristol."},"image_url":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/{recipe}/p0c4krx5.jpg","duration":{"value":1680,"label":"28 mins"},"progress":null,"availability":{"from":"2022-05-17T16:00:15Z","to":null,"label":"Available for over a year"},"container":{"type":"brand","id":"b006qxsb","urn":"urn:bbc:radio:brand:b006qxsb","title":"Great Lives","synopses":{"short":"Biographical series in which guests choose someone who has inspired their lives.","medium":"Biographical series in which guests choose someone who has inspired their lives.","long":null},"activities":[]},"uris":[{"type":"latest","id":null,"label":"Latest","uri":"/v2/programmes/playable?container=b006qxsb&sort=sequential&type=episode&experience=domestic"}],"activities":[],"play_context":null,"guidance":{"competition_warning":false,"warnings":null},"recommendation":null},{"id":"m0017kgn","type":"playable_item","urn":"urn:bbc:radio:episode:m0017kgp","network":{"id":"bbc_radio_four","key":"radio4","short_title":"Radio 4","logo_url":"https://sounds.files.bbci.co.uk/3.5.0/networks/bbc_radio_four/{type}_{size}.{format}","network_type":"master_brand"},"release":{"date":"2022-05-24T00:00:00Z","label":"24 May 2022"},"titles":{"primary":"Great Lives","secondary":"Joan Rhodes, strongest woman in the world","tertiary":null,"entity_title":"Joan Rhodes, strongest woman in the world"},"synopses":{"short":"Anna Maxwell Martin proposes Joan Rhodes, variety artiste and strongwoman","medium":"One of the more unexpected choices - Joan Rhodes was also known as the Mighty Mannequin 